## 9. ESCALATION TRIGGERS

STOP and ask human if:
- [ ] Instructions conflict with Master Calibration
- [ ] Destructive operation (delete, migrate, overwrite)
- [ ] Cannot verify with deterministic test
- [ ] Context exceeds token limits
- [ ] Sync system not working (current active issue)
- [ ] Test timeout despite "correct" code
- [ ] Need to install unapproved dependency
- [ ] Modifying frozen zone (VideoInput.tsx)
- [ ] Changing AI prompt affecting instructional design
- [ ] API key or encryption changes

